{
  "id": "5c6cca12df4d480017b52539",
  "title": "ロジカルシンキングの悪用",
  "created": 1550633495,
  "updated": 1554446664,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c6cca12df4d480017b52539",
      "text": "ロジカルシンキングの悪用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633495,
      "updated": 1550633498
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca1aaff09e000053e072",
      "text": "[ロジカルシンキング]は悪用されているケースがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633498,
      "updated": 1550633890
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca53aff09e000053e074",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633556,
      "updated": 1550633556
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca54aff09e000053e075",
      "text": "ロジックによって[基礎付け]ることができる、という素朴な信念は誤っていて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633557,
      "updated": 1550633897
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca6faff09e000053e076",
      "text": " 公理が正しいかどうか不明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633584,
      "updated": 1550633603
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca83aff09e000053e077",
      "text": " [無限後退]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633604,
      "updated": 1554446664
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca90aff09e000053e078",
      "text": "など",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633617,
      "updated": 1550633623
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca96aff09e000053e079",
      "text": "[ミュンヒハウゼンのトリレンマ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633623,
      "updated": 1550633634
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccaa4aff09e000053e07a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633636,
      "updated": 1550633636
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccaa6aff09e000053e07b",
      "text": "これを悪意を持って使えば、遅延させたいプロジェクトに対する[サボタージュ]ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633638,
      "updated": 1550633843
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccac7aff09e000053e07c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633671,
      "updated": 1550633671
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccac7aff09e000053e07d",
      "text": "その上で自分はロジックに基づかない裁量を行使して成果を出し「[成果による能力の証明]」というロジックに持ち込むことができる。[プラグマティズム]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633672,
      "updated": 1550633871
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccb02aff09e000053e07e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633730,
      "updated": 1550633730
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccb02aff09e000053e07f",
      "text": "こういう単純で有害な戦略は、簡単に止められるかと思っていたが、意外とこういう[正しさの相対化]の話を理解できなかったり、なぜか感情的に反発したりする人がいて驚いた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633730,
      "updated": 1550633815
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccb5baff09e000053e080",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633819,
      "updated": 1550633819
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6ccb5baff09e000053e081",
      "text": "単にそういうシステム、力学、の話に過ぎないのだが…。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633819,
      "updated": 1550633838
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6cca49aff09e000053e073",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550633545,
      "updated": 1550633545
    }
  ]
}